<http://www.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/event/10802AKDPPJLQDDGMGRRMQHBTKBDQPLRL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name " Pien d’amoroso affetto / With Amorous Affections";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Pien d’amoroso affetto / With Amorous Affections</h1><span><br/></span><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/files/f298b785-94fa-40df-8135-ffb5111a69b6.jpg\" /><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Acclaimed vocalist Marc Mauillon and harpist Angélique Mauillon take you a journey through the music of Renaissance Florence and Paris, to discover the origins and evolution of the opera. The birth of opera is traced through composers such as Giulio Caccini, Jacopo Peri, and composers of the ‘airs de cour’ Sébastien Le Camus and Michel Lambert, inspired by the poetry of Henriette de Coligny. Join them for this deeply personal and refined exploration of music’s most passionate form.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-08-04T13:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/files/f298b785-94fa-40df-8135-ffb5111a69b6.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/location/401ANPJQJQPQMRSBDNMVNLSPGTRBVQVRH>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/organization/early-music-vancouver>;
  schema:url <https://www.earlymusic.bc.ca/events/pien-damoroso-affetto-with-amorous-affections/>;
  schema:offers _:78f1e3f00e524974ab72909aa5a3a4a92981;
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-08-04T14:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

